correctness.rationale: The extraction contains multiple schema violations, ungrounded entries, and incorrect values. Key issues: (1) Numerous numeric fields are null (schema requires numbers): processParameters.pressure.quantityValue.numericValue; thicknessControl.growthPerCycle.numberofCycles.quantityValue.numericValue; nucleationPeriod.quantityValue.numericValue; all dosingTime and purgeTime numericValues; all flowRates numericValues; multiple materialProperties (refractiveIndex, absorptionCoefficient, bandGap, resistivity, carrierDensity, mobility, conformality.aspectRatio, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values, roughness.value, filmDensity.value); deviceProperties.fieldEffectMobility and onOffRatio. (2) GPC is incorrect by an order of magnitude and unit: article reports ~0.21 nm/cycle; extraction uses 0.21 Å/cycle for each suboxide. Correct to 2.1 Å/cycle (or 0.21 nm/cycle) and avoid per-compound values not reported. (3) Film thickness set to 20 nm appears to conflate IGZO with the 20 nm IZO gate electrode; IGZO thickness is not reported—both processParameters.filmThickness and thicknessControl.filmThickness should be corrected or removed if not known (but schema currently requires them). (4) Substrate listed as “SiO2/Si” is unsubstantiated; deposition occurs on a patterned Mo/SiO2/Mo BEOL stack (hole sidewalls). (5) CarrierGas and purgingGas set to “Not Found” (required by schema but not reported in article); these should be either correctly identified (e.g., N2/Ar if stated) or flagged as missing—placeholders are not acceptable. (6) “Saturation” set to true without support from the text. (7) AtomicRatio 1:1:1 is presented as measured composition, but the article only specifies a deposition cycle ratio 1:1:1; replace with measured composition if available or omit. (8) Supercycle sequence is fixed as InOx→GaOx→ZnOx, but the article discusses varying sequences and does not state a single chosen sequence—this should be grounded or removed. (9) OtherAspects.filmStability and reproducibility set to true are not supported by the text. Correct entries include: ALD method (PEALD), reactor (TFS200), co-reactant (O2 plasma), temperature (250 °C), plasma power (38 W), uniformity variation (1.26%), device threshold voltage (-3.5 V) and SS (230 mV/dec), and device structure (CAA). Overall, due to extensive nulls (schema violations), several untraceable or incorrect values, and misinterpretations, the extraction quality is very poor and requires substantial correction.

completeness.rationale: Several schema-required fields are present but populated with invalid or placeholder values, and some entries conflict with the article. Key issues: (1) Multiple numeric fields are null (schema requires numbers, and extraction must avoid null): processParameters.pressure.quantityValue.numericValue; thicknessControl.numberofCycles; nucleationPeriod.quantityValue.numericValue; all dosingTime and purgeTime numericValues; all flowRates numericValues; materialProperties.conformality.aspectRatio; roughness.value; filmDensity.value; deviceProperties.fieldEffectMobility and onOffRatio. (2) Growth-per-cycle is incorrect in unit and context: article reports ~0.21 nm/cycle for IGZO vs supercycle; extraction uses 0.21 Å per compound, which is a 10× underestimation and not traceable per element. (3) Film thickness of 20 nm is likely misassigned to IGZO; the article states 20 nm for the IZO gate electrode, not the IGZO channel. (4) ReactantSelection carrierGas and purgingGas are set to 'Not Found' (placeholders) with no article support; similarly many 'Not Found' fields (e.g., deliveryMethod, reactor.manufacturer) reduce completeness/traceability. (5) Substrate listed as 'SiO2/Si' is not explicitly stated; the article describes a MIM stack and 8-inch wafer but not a Si substrate choice—this should be verified. (6) Film composition atomicRatio '1:1:1' is taken from cycle ratio, not a measured composition; elementalConcentration lacks values; crystallinity 'amorphous' is not explicitly reported with a method. (7) OtherAspects filmStability=True and reproducibility=True are not supported by explicit statements. Correct items include PEALD method, TFS200 reactor, O2 plasma co-reactant, 250 °C, plasma power 38 W, and the 1:1:1 supercycle ratio, and uniformity 1.26%. To improve completeness: populate pressure, cycle counts, dosing/purge times, and flow rates; correct GPC to ~0.21 nm/cycle with proper context; correct or remove IGZO film thickness unless reported; verify substrate; provide measured composition or remove atomicRatio if not measured; add conformality metric if available; remove unsupported booleans or justify them; and provide device on/off ratio if reported.
